# Cloudflare API token untuk penerbitan sertifikat HTTPS (Caddy DNS-01).
#
# Cara pakai di Raspberry Pi:
#   sudo cp cloudflare.env.example /etc/caddy/cloudflare.env
#   sudo nano /etc/caddy/cloudflare.env      # tempel token asli
#   sudo chmod 600 /etc/caddy/cloudflare.env
#   sudo bash setup.sh https                 # Caddy pakai sertifikat asli
#
# Cara membuat token (sekali saja):
#   1. https://dash.cloudflare.com  ->  ikon profil  ->  "My Profile"
#   2. tab "API Tokens"  ->  "Create Token"
#   3. pakai template "Edit zone DNS"
#   4. Permissions : Zone > DNS > Edit
#      Zone Resources: Include > Specific zone > wipevision.my.id
#   5. Create Token  ->  SALIN token (hanya ditampilkan sekali)
#
# CATATAN KEAMANAN: file /etc/caddy/cloudflare.env JANGAN di-commit ke git.
CF_API_TOKEN=ISI_TOKEN_CLOUDFLARE_DISINI
